Introduction

Homme (Korean: 옴므; Japanese: オム) was a male duo under Big Hit Entertainment. Consisting of 8Eight's Lee Hyun and 2AM's Changmin, they debuted on July 28, 2010 with the single "Homme by "Hitman" Bang".
